page.title: 14Tradespeople.
page.content: We will list,looking in each direction from the square,all shops to the left then all shops on other side coming back towards the square: MARKET ST.:Wholefoods,Butchers,Books,Grocers, Restaurant,then Restaurant,Hairdresser,Ironmonger,Chem ist and Bank.(another Butcher and Grocer towards Church.) EAST ST.:Bank,Baker,Shoes,Restaurant,Petrol ,Pub.,Exchange,Woodcraft,Buses then Ironmonger,Craft,Picture Framing,Pub. BRIDGE/WEST ST.: Grocer,then Milk(Cnwce),Garage,Garage,Pub.,Library ,Pub.,(PARROG RD.Potter,Grocer,Club.) LONG ST.: Post Office,Newsagents,Clothing,then General Stores,Carpets,Energy Group/Nat.Park Information,Craft.
